title: Manson Shooting Victim Dies
content: The victim of last weeks shooting in Manson has died. The Chelan County Sheriff’s Office reports 23 year old Anna Sanchez died at Providence Sacred Heart Medical Center in Spokane where she had been airlifted after suffering a gunshot wound to the head last Thursday. Undersheriff Jason Mathews said last week that after deputies had interviewed two other occupants of the residence at the time of the incident, the shooting appeared to be accidental. Deputies responded last Thursday at 3 a.m. and found Sanchez in the bedroom of a residence in the Lakeview Trailer Park on Hwy 150 with a gunshot wound to the head.
